## Description

And talk about marathon swimmers, these guys would give Michael Phelps a run, or rather a swim, for his money, clocking speeds up to 37 mph! Plus, their social skills put ours to shame; imagine throwing a party with thousands of your best pals, that's just any Tuesday for them. And let's not neglect their unique "half asleep, half awake" napping style because, well, who needs a full night's rest when there's fun to be had under the sea?
